name: gChart
body:
# gChart
gChart is a simple Wrapper to Google's Visualization API (Google Charts). This is made for simple integration for beginners to take advantage of Google's great visualization's in  any web application. This is still in pre-alpha and will have some issues, however feel free to play with it!

# Issues
If any issues are not listed please create them or email [Bradd Schick](mailto:bradd.schick@gmail.com) with the issue details. Thanks!
